  "title": "Cloud Network Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Cloud Network Engineer</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Manage Cloud Network Infrastructure.</strong></li><li><strong>Good in handling Cloud maintenance, support, deployment & implementation.</strong></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Strong in Cloud Infrastructure (AWS, Azure etc).</strong></li><li><strong>Good in Network Infrastructure.</strong></li><li>Good in handling Cloud Infrastructure (AWS, Azure)</li><li>Min. 2 years Cloud Netwrok Infrastructure experience</li><li>Good in handling Cloud Computing, Virtulisation,</li><li>Possess Cisco certification.</li><li><strong>Expereince in Cloud SaaS, IaaS etc.</strong></li><li>Strong understanding of security best practices in Cloud, Azure, AWS, Microsoft 365</li><li>Possess Cloud certification (AWS /Azure / GCP) is preferred.</li><li>Singaporean Only!</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>We respect your privacy and all communication will be treated with confidentiality.</p><p>Please contact us or apply in-confidence to us with you updated MS Word Resume to : jeline@starcareerconsulting.com</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Yong Jeline (Reg. No. R1101621)</p><p>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD (EA License: 20C0353)</p>",
